Guidelime.registerGuide(
[[
[N40-41 Badlands]
[GA Horde]
[D A guide created by T H A C E N#9446\Based on Joana's Speed Leveling guide https://www.joanasworld.com]
First Pick the Class you are playing top left of screen!!!
01) As you enter Badlands, grind your way SW to Valley of Fangs and turn in "[QT1106 Martek the Exiled]" ([G42,53]), accept "[QA1108 Indurium]". Next to you, accept "[QA703 Barbecued Buzzard Wings]". And if you have 9 Blue Pearls with you, accept and turn in "[QT705 Pearl Diving]".
02) Go south a bit (around [G51,67]) and do "[QC1108 Indurium]": kill/loot the Stonevault troggs.
03) Go back north to Valley of Fangs and turn in "[QT1108 Indurium]" ([G42,53], #1 on map). Wait a few seconds then accept "[QA1137 News for Fizzle]".
04) Go NW to The Dustbowl, and at the gnome ([G26,45]), accept "[QA710 Study of the Elements: Rock]". If you have a Frost Oil item, accept and complete the quest "[QC713 Coolant Heads Prevail]". Then if you have a Gyrochronatom item, accept and complete the quest "[QC714 Gyro... What?]".
05) Grind west to Kargath and get the FP there from the Wind Rider Master ([G4,45]). NOTE: Keep your Hearthstone set to Grom'gol!
06) Go up the watchtower and accept "[QA1419 Coyote Thieves]" and "[QA1420 Report to Helgrum]" ([G7,47]).
07) Go in the Inn ([G3,46]) and accept "[QA782 Broken Alliances]" and (upstairs) "[QA2258 Badlands Reagent Run]". Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
08) Do "[QC710 Study of the Elements: Rock]" kill/loot Lesser Rock Elementals up north on the cliffs (around [G19,42]).
09) Go to The Dustbowl at the gnome ([G26,45], #4 on map) and turn in "[QT710 Study of the Elements: Rock]", accept the next [QA711 part].
10) Grind your way south and do "[QC711 Study of the Elements: Rock]": kill/loot Rock Elementals (around [G41,78]).
11) Grind your way north to The Dustbowl at the gnome ([G26,45], #4 on map) and turn in "[QT711 Study of the Elements: Rock]", accept the next [QA712 part].
12) Do the following 4 steps below (in any order) around the western part of Badlands:
13) "[QC782 Broken Alliances]": kill/loot Boss Tho'grun /target. This ogre patrols in a large circle counter-clockwise around the SW part of Badlands. He has 5 bodyguards. Pull/kite him away from his guards to take him on 1v1. (See Video). NOTE: You can focus on the next steps until he shows up...
14) "[QC703 Barbecued Buzzard Wings]": kill/loot Buzzards. There is a large amount of Giant Buzzards at ([G16,61]). And remember to not sell the Buzzard Wings to a vendor.
15) "[QC1419 Coyote Thieves]": kill/loot Coyotes. Focus more on the Elder Crag Coyotes around the western side of Badlands.
16) "[QC2258 Badlands Reagent Run]": kill/loot Buzzards, Coyotes and Rock Elementals. This quest will naturally get done by doing the others.
17) Go south and do "[QC712 Study of the Elements: Rock]": kill/loot Greater Rock Elementals (around [G15,88]).
18) Once all that is done, go back to Kargath, and up in the watchtower ([G7,47]), turn in "[QT1419 Coyote Thieves]".
19) Go in the Inn ([G3,46]) and turn in "[QT782 Broken Alliances]", SKIP the next part (high level group quest).
20) Go upstairs and turn in "[QT2258 Badlands Reagent Run]", SKIP the next part (group quest). Make sure you are repaired/resupplied.
21) Go east to The Dustbowl at the gnome ([G26,45]) and turn in "[QT712 Study of the Elements: Rock]". If it is available, accept "[QA734 This Is Going To Be Hard]", and turn it in right next to you and accept the next [QA777 part]. Turn that in right next to you and accept the next [QA778 part]. Kill/loot the Fam'retor Guardian that spawns in. Then turn it in.
22) Also, if you have a Healing Potion and a Lesser Invisibility Potion with you, accept (if it is available) "[QA715 Liquid Stone]", then turn it in.
23) And also if you have a Patterned Bronze Bracers with you, accept (if it is available) "[QA716 Stone Is Better than Cloth]", then turn it in.
24) Go east (in the middle of Badlands) and turn in "[QT703 Barbecued Buzzard Wings]" ([G42,53]).
25) Grind your way east to Lethlor Ravine ([G70,53]) to discover it for XP and then grind on Scalding Whelps for a bit. Watch out for the elite Scorched Guardians! Make sure you are level 41, if not keep grinding on the whelps (or any mob in the Badlands) until you are.
26) Hearth to Grom'gol.
27) Make sure you are repaired/resupplied. 
28) Now could be a good time to see if you have all the pages for "The Green Hills of Stranglethorn". This quest requires that you have the following pages: 1, 4, 6, 8, 10, 11, 14, 16, 18, 20, 21, 24, 25, 26, and 27. You can also find these pages in the AH or from other players. If you have all of them, get them out now and go to Nesingwary's Expedition ([G36,11]) and turn this quest in. If not, you will return to STV numerous times in the future for more chances to find the pages.
29) Run all the way to Swamp of Sorrows, stopping along the way at Beggar's Haunt to accept "[QA1372 Nothing But the Truth]" (in Duskwood at [G88,35]).
30) Next to you, turn in "[QT1372 Nothing But the Truth]", accept the next [QA1383 part].
31) Run east through Deadwind Pass, follow the main path and then make a left into Ariden's Camp ([G51,39] in Deadwind Pass) just to discover it for XP.
32) Continue east into Swamp of Sorrows...
[NX 41-42 Swamp of Sorrows]
]], "Thacen")
